{
  "texts": [
    "We also propose a rubric-based RL pipeline RIFL, which first generates rubrics for complex instructions, then trains a rubric verifier to provide feedback, and finally optimizes the LLM with RL.",
    "Our experiments show that RIFL significantly improves the IF ability of LLMs.",
    "We also conduct extensive ablation studies to validate the effectiveness of each component in our pipeline.",
    "Our work demonstrates the potential of using rubrics as a powerful tool for training and evaluating LLMs, and opens up new avenues for future research in this direction.",
    "We hope our work can inspire more research on improving the instruction-following ability of LLMs, and contribute to the development of more capable and reliable AI systems."
  ]
}